Help for LOGONNEWS:

LOGONNEWS manages logon news sent by Services to users when they connect.
Note that the title/subject of the news post can only be one word.

Syntax: LOGONNEWS ADD|DEL|LIST [title] [message]

Examples:
	/msg &nick& LOGONNEWS ADD News1 Some important logonnews for users.
	/msg &nick& LOGONNEWS ADD News2 Some less important logonnews for users.
	/msg &nick& LOGONNEWS LIST
	/msg &nick& LOGONNEWS DEL 2
